Name: alterator-net-eth
Version: 5.1.0
Release: alt1

Source:%name-%version.tar

Summary: alterator module for tcp/ip connections configuration
License: GPL
Group: System/Configuration/Other
Requires: alterator >= 5.0 libshell >= 0.1.3
